Three products. Three intensities. From beginner to expert, level up your eye looks with The Climax Collection. Field Trainer for NARS UK & ROI, @renatomkp, shows you how in this three-part series for every skill level. 

LEVEL 3: DARING DIMENSION 
TO PREP: 
Radiant Creamy Concealer in Custard
Light Reflecting Setting Powder in Crystal

TO SEDUCE:
“When doing a graphic eyeliner look, create the shape first. Outline a path using Aqua-Infused Makeup Removing Water and an angled brush. This will act as a guide when drawing your liner.” —@renatomkp

High-Pigment Longwear Eyelier in Via Veneto
Climax Eyeshadow Palette in shade Passion Play
Aqua-Infused Makeup Removing Water 
Climax Liquid Eyeliner
